Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:03.94,English,,0,0,0,,Your DNA is probably already in a database.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:03.94,Chinese,,0,0,0,,你的 DNA 可能已经在一个数据库当中了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.94,0:00:07.17,English,,0,0,0,,You didn't have to provide a sample or give consent
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.94,0:00:07.17,Chinese,,0,0,0,,你无需提供样本或者给予许可
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.17,0:00:11.93,English,,0,0,0,,but the unique sequence of As, Ts, Gs and Cs that make you you
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.17,0:00:11.93,Chinese,,0,0,0,,但你拥有的四种碱基 (A T G和C) 的独特序列
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.93,0:00:13.87,English,,0,0,0,,are searchable nonetheless.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.93,0:00:13.87,Chinese,,0,0,0,,是可以被检索到的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.87,0:00:15.77,English,,0,0,0,,So if you committed a heinous crime
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.87,0:00:15.77,Chinese,,0,0,0,,所以  如果你犯下了令人发指的罪行
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.77,0:00:17.35,English,,0,0,0,,and left a bit of your DNA,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.77,0:00:17.35,Chinese,,0,0,0,,并留下了你哪怕只有一点的DNA
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.35,0:00:20.05,English,,0,0,0,,law enforcement could search it in a database
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.35,0:00:20.05,Chinese,,0,0,0,,执法部门就可以在数据库中对你的DNA进行检索
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.05,0:00:21.43,English,,0,0,0,,and identify you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.05,0:00:21.43,Chinese,,0,0,0,,并最终识别到你的身份
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.90,0:00:28.06,English,,0,0,0,,This video includes a discussion of serious crimes which may be disturbing for some viewers
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.90,0:00:28.06,Chinese,,0,0,0,,本视频包括一些可能令观众感到不安的严重罪行的讨论
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.06,0:00:30.60,English,,0,0,0,,so I wanted to let you know that upfront,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.06,0:00:30.60,Chinese,,0,0,0,,所以我想提前告知您
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.60,0:00:36.81,English,,0,0,0,,but I think it's necessary to talk about these crimes in some detail for reasons that will become apparent.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.60,0:00:36.81,Chinese,,0,0,0,,但由于即将显而易见的原因  我认为有必要详细讨论这些犯罪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.26,0:00:43.43,English,,0,0,0,,In the small town of Visalia, California in the mid 1970s,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.26,0:00:43.43,Chinese,,0,0,0,,上世纪70年代中期  在加利福尼亚州维塞利亚小镇
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.43,0:00:46.94,English,,0,0,0,,one of the state's most prolific criminals got his start.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.43,0:00:46.94,Chinese,,0,0,0,,该州犯罪最多的罪犯之一开始了他的犯罪生涯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.94,0:00:53.47,English,,0,0,0,,He repeatedly broke into houses and stole small items like cash, coins, and jewelry.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.94,0:00:53.47,Chinese,,0,0,0,,他多次闯入民宅并偷走现金 硬币和珠宝等小物件
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.47,0:00:56.46,English,,0,0,0,,He was dubbed the Visalia ransacker
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.47,0:00:56.46,Chinese,,0,0,0,,他被称为“维塞利亚劫掠者”
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.46,0:00:59.29,English,,0,0,0,,but soon his crimes escalated.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.46,0:00:59.29,Chinese,,0,0,0,,但很快他的罪行就不止于此了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.29,0:01:01.22,English,,0,0,0,,- Six months later in 1976,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.29,0:01:01.22,Chinese,,0,0,0,,六个月后的1976年
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.22,0:01:02.96,English,,0,0,0,,he moves up to Sacramento and over
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.22,0:01:02.96,Chinese,,0,0,0,,他搬去了萨克拉门托
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.96,0:01:04.56,English,,0,0,0,,the course of the next three years,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.96,0:01:04.56,Chinese,,0,0,0,,并且在接下来的三年里
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.56,0:01:12.66,English,,0,0,0,,he's moving all across Northern California committing numerous sexual assaults, over 50 sexual assaults.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.56,0:01:12.66,Chinese,,0,0,0,,他在北加州多地犯下了超过50起强奸案
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.66,0:01:15.60,English,,0,0,0,,- Here, he was called the east area rapist.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.66,0:01:15.60,Chinese,,0,0,0,,在这里  他被称为“东区强暴魔”
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.60,0:01:17.87,English,,0,0,0,,- [Male Reporter] The police are saying lock up tight.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.60,0:01:17.87,Chinese,,0,0,0,,警察说要锁紧门窗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.87,0:01:21.26,English,,0,0,0,,Sacramento's infamous east area rapist may still be in town.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.87,0:01:21.26,Chinese,,0,0,0,,因为萨拉克门托臭名昭著的“东区强暴魔”可能还在城里
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.28,0:01:26.06,English,,0,0,0,,- And then in 1979, he moves down to Southern California,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.28,0:01:26.06,Chinese,,0,0,0,,然后在1979年  他搬去南加州
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.06,0:01:29.31,English,,0,0,0,,starting in Santa Barbara and starts killing.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.06,0:01:29.31,Chinese,,0,0,0,,从圣巴巴拉开始杀人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.31,0:01:32.78,English,,0,0,0,,And he was known as the original night stalker in Southern California.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.31,0:01:32.78,Chinese,,0,0,0,,他被称为南加州的“暗夜尾行者”
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.78,0:01:37.04,English,,0,0,0,,- [Reporter] Variously known as the east area rapist and the original night stalker,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.78,0:01:37.04,Chinese,,0,0,0,,他被人们称为“东区强暴魔”“暗夜尾行者”
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.04,0:01:45.69,English,,0,0,0,,these were brutal meticulously planned crimes that spanned numerous California counties between 1976 and 1986.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.04,0:01:45.69,Chinese,,0,0,0,,这些是1976年至1986年间  跨越加利福尼亚州多县  精心策划的残酷犯罪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.69,0:01:52.84,English,,0,0,0,,- Police believed that all of these crimes were committed by the same person now known as the golden state killer.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.69,0:01:52.84,Chinese,,0,0,0,,警察相信  所有这些罪行都是由现在被称为“金州杀手”的同一人所犯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.84,0:01:56.01,English,,0,0,0,,How was it known that these were committed by the same person?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.84,0:01:56.01,Chinese,,0,0,0,,如何知道这些都是由同一人所犯的呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.01,0:01:58.84,English,,0,0,0,,- Investigators were relying on MO.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.01,0:01:58.84,Chinese,,0,0,0,,调查人员们依赖 MO
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.24,0:02:05.65,English,,0,0,0,,MO, modus operandi is basically how a criminal will commit a crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.24,0:02:05.65,Chinese,,0,0,0,,MO（作案手法）这个词  大概意思是“犯罪分子是如何犯罪的”
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.65,0:02:09.03,English,,0,0,0,,- He was wearing some type of a mask or a hood.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.65,0:02:09.03,Chinese,,0,0,0,,他戴着某种面具或者兜帽
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.73,0:02:11.97,English,,0,0,0,,He was wearing shorts and a T-shirt.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.73,0:02:11.97,Chinese,,0,0,0,,他穿着短裤和T恤衫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.97,0:02:14.65,English,,0,0,0,,- The golden state killer had a very distinctive MO
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.97,0:02:14.65,Chinese,,0,0,0,,“金州杀手”的作案手法非常独特
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.65,0:02:15.55,English,,0,0,0,,- What he would do is
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.65,0:02:15.55,Chinese,,0,0,0,,他会做的是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.55,0:02:19.10,English,,0,0,0,,he would break into a house with a gun,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.10,0:02:21.21,English,,0,0,0,,a house with a man and a woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.55,0:02:21.21,Chinese,,0,0,0,,持枪闯入一栋有男人和女人的民宅
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.21,0:02:23.03,English,,0,0,0,,He would tie them up
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.21,0:02:23.03,Chinese,,0,0,0,,把他们绑起来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.06,0:02:27.22,English,,0,0,0,,tell the man I'm gonna put plates on your back.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.06,0:02:27.22,Chinese,,0,0,0,,然后告诉那个男人  我要把盘子放到你的后背上
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.22,0:02:28.70,English,,0,0,0,,If I hear those plates move,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.22,0:02:28.70,Chinese,,0,0,0,,如果我听到盘子动了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.70,0:02:31.40,English,,0,0,0,,I'm going to kill your wife and then kill you,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.70,0:02:31.40,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我就要杀了你的妻子然后再杀了你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.40,0:02:34.47,English,,0,0,0,,take the wife into another room and sexually assault her.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.40,0:02:34.47,Chinese,,0,0,0,,他把妻子带到另一个房间对她进行性侵犯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.47,0:02:38.90,English,,0,0,0,,Then he would go through the house for however much time,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.47,0:02:38.90,Chinese,,0,0,0,,然后他会在房子里徘徊相当久
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.90,0:02:42.11,English,,0,0,0,,eating, stealing stuff, stealing little things or whatever
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.90,0:02:42.11,Chinese,,0,0,0,,就吃东西  偷东西之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.11,0:02:43.42,English,,0,0,0,,and then he would leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.11,0:02:43.42,Chinese,,0,0,0,,然后他才会离开
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.42,0:02:46.90,English,,0,0,0,,- How was he not caught based on fingerprint evidence?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.42,0:02:46.90,Chinese,,0,0,0,,他怎么没因为指纹证据被抓？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.90,0:02:48.88,English,,0,0,0,,- Well, he didn't leave his fingerprints.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.90,0:02:48.88,Chinese,,0,0,0,,好吧  他没留下指纹
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.88,0:02:49.94,English,,0,0,0,,He always wore a mask.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.88,0:02:49.94,Chinese,,0,0,0,,他总是戴着面具
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.94,0:02:51.14,English,,0,0,0,,He always had gloves on.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.94,0:02:51.14,Chinese,,0,0,0,,他总是戴着手套
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.14,0:02:53.75,English,,0,0,0,,This was an offender that did everything
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.75,0:02:55.73,English,,0,0,0,,to prevent himself from being caught.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.14,0:02:55.73,Chinese,,0,0,0,,这是一个竭尽全力防止自己被抓的罪犯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.73,0:02:58.90,English,,0,0,0,,- [Reporter] The golden state killer has been linked to at least 12 murders,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.73,0:02:58.90,Chinese,,0,0,0,,“金州杀手”与在加州发生的至少12起谋杀案
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.90,0:03:02.49,English,,0,0,0,,50 rapes, and a string of burglaries throughout California.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.90,0:03:02.49,Chinese,,0,0,0,,50起强奸案和一系列的盗窃案有关
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.40,0:03:07.81,English,,0,0,0,,- All right, how's it going?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.40,0:03:07.81,Chinese,,0,0,0,,最近怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.81,0:03:09.09,English,,0,0,0,,- How you doing? - Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.81,0:03:09.09,Chinese,,0,0,0,,你好吗？ 好的好的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.09,0:03:12.76,English,,0,0,0,,- So we supply DNA sequencing solutions
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.76,0:03:15.97,English,,0,0,0,,to the forensic laboratories that process crime scene DNA.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.34,0:03:15.97,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我们为处理犯罪现场 DNA 的法医实验室提供 DNA 测序解决方案
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.97,0:03:21.01,English,,0,0,0,,At a crime scene, there's typically less than a nanogram of DNA left
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.97,0:03:21.01,Chinese,,0,0,0,,一般我们在犯罪现场  只能找到不到1纳克的 DNA
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.01,0:03:23.24,English,,0,0,0,,and it's usually degraded, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.01,0:03:23.24,Chinese,,0,0,0,,并且它们通常还会降解  对吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.97,0:03:23.24,Chinese,,0,0,0,,{\an7\pos(2596,1802)}纳克{\fsp-24}：{\fsp0}10的-9次方克{\fsp-24}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.24,0:03:24.00,English,,0,0,0,,So it breaks down.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.24,0:03:24.00,Chinese,,0,0,0,,所以它降解了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.00,0:03:25.97,English,,0,0,0,,- Why is there so little? at a crime scene?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.00,0:03:25.97,Chinese,,0,0,0,,为什么在犯罪现场  只有这么少？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.97,0:03:27.13,English,,0,0,0,,A nanogram?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.97,0:03:27.13,Chinese,,0,0,0,,只有1纳克？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.13,0:03:27.63,English,,0,0,0,,- Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.13,0:03:27.63,Chinese,,0,0,0,,对的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.63,0:03:28.49,English,,0,0,0,,- That's insane.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.63,0:03:28.49,Chinese,,0,0,0,,这太疯狂了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.49,0:03:29.23,English,,0,0,0,,- Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.49,0:03:29.23,Chinese,,0,0,0,,对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.23,0:03:32.62,English,,0,0,0,,- There's no accident that he stops in 1986.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.23,0:03:32.62,Chinese,,0,0,0,,他在1986年停止作案绝非偶然
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.62,0:03:38.32,English,,0,0,0,,1986 is when the first DNA case... of a murder case
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.62,0:03:38.32,Chinese,,0,0,0,,1986年  第一次有通过 DNA 破解的…一桩谋杀案
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.32,0:03:41.61,English,,0,0,0,,is actually solved with DNA and he's,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.32,0:03:41.61,Chinese,,0,0,0,,是用 DNA 解决的  嗯…他…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.61,0:03:45.22,English,,0,0,0,,I think he's following that and he's saying, you know what,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.61,0:03:45.22,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我觉得他正在跟进这些案件的进度  他说  你知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.22,0:03:49.09,English,,0,0,0,,what I'm doing here, I'm leaving my DNA.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.22,0:03:49.09,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我在这做的事  会遗留下我的 DNA
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.09,0:03:50.61,English,,0,0,0,,I can't do this anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.09,0:03:50.61,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我可再也不能犯罪了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.61,0:03:54.33,English,,0,0,0,,- [Reporter] Investigator Paul Holes tracked the golden state killer for decades.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.61,0:03:54.33,Chinese,,0,0,0,,调查员保罗·霍尔斯追查了“金州杀手”几十年
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.33,0:03:56.35,English,,0,0,0,,- He couldn't account for DNA technology
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.33,0:03:56.35,Chinese,,0,0,0,,他不了解 DNA 技术
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.35,0:03:58.40,English,,0,0,0,,and that really was his big mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.35,0:03:58.40,Chinese,,0,0,0,,这确实是他犯下的大错
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.40,0:04:00.01,English,,0,0,0,,That was the critical mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.40,0:04:00.01,Chinese,,0,0,0,,这是个严重的错误
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.01,0:04:03.03,English,,0,0,0,,He left his DNA all over California.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.01,0:04:03.03,Chinese,,0,0,0,,他把他的 DNA 留得整个加州到处都是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.03,0:04:05.20,English,,0,0,0,,And it turns out that in three of the cases,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.03,0:04:05.20,Chinese,,0,0,0,,事实证明  在其中三个案例中
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.20,0:04:07.66,English,,0,0,0,,I had three sexual assault kits and that's where I got
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.66,0:04:10.92,English,,0,0,0,,the golden state killer's DNA from Northern California.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.20,0:04:10.92,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我有三个性侵验伤包  这就是我从北加州获得“金州杀手” DNA 的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.20,0:04:10.92,Chinese,,0,0,0,,{\an7\pos(396,1610)}性侵工具包{\fsp0}：\N{\fsp0}一种取证工具{\fsp0}  能帮助受害者快速留下被性侵证据{\fsp0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.35,0:04:15.70,English,,0,0,0,,- But having the unknown killer's DNA wasn't enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.35,0:04:15.70,Chinese,,0,0,0,,但只有未知杀手的 DNA 还不够
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.70,0:04:18.33,English,,0,0,0,,They needed to match it to a known sample.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.70,0:04:18.33,Chinese,,0,0,0,,他们还需将其与已知样本匹配起来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.11,0:04:21.64,English,,0,0,0,,In 1990, the FBI started work
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.11,0:04:21.64,Chinese,,0,0,0,,1990年  FBI (美国联邦调查局)
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.64,0:04:24.83,English,,0,0,0,,on what would become a national genetic database.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.64,0:04:24.83,Chinese,,0,0,0,,开始建立全国的基因库
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.83,0:04:26.83,English,,0,0,0,,It mainly stores DNA profiles
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.83,0:04:26.83,Chinese,,0,0,0,,这个基因库主要记录已被判刑的罪犯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.83,0:04:29.81,English,,0,0,0,,from convicted criminals and persons of interest.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.83,0:04:29.81,Chinese,,0,0,0,,和案件相关人士的 DNA 档案
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.81,0:04:32.91,English,,0,0,0,,It's called the combined DNA index system
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.81,0:04:32.91,Chinese,,0,0,0,,它被称为“联合 DNA 索引系统” 
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.91,0:04:35.13,English,,0,0,0,,or CODIS for short.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.91,0:04:35.13,Chinese,,0,0,0,,缩写是 CODIS
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.13,0:04:38.81,English,,0,0,0,,In each of your cells, there are 23 pairs of chromosomes,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.13,0:04:38.81,Chinese,,0,0,0,,你的每一个细胞中  都有23对染色体
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.81,0:04:41.49,English,,0,0,0,,one from your mom and one from your dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.81,0:04:41.49,Chinese,,0,0,0,,一对染色体中有一条来自母亲  另一条来自父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.49,0:04:43.96,English,,0,0,0,,And at particular places on some chromosomes,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.49,0:04:43.96,Chinese,,0,0,0,,在某些染色体中的特定位置上
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.96,0:04:46.48,English,,0,0,0,,there are short sections of DNA that repeat
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.96,0:04:46.48,Chinese,,0,0,0,,会有一些重复的 DNA 片段 
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.97,0:04:52.97,English with background,,0,0,0,,like A A T G, A A T G, A A T G, and so on.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.97,0:04:52.97,Chinese with background,,0,0,0,,像是 AATG AATG AATG 这样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.06,0:04:57.20,English with background,,0,0,0,,These are called short tandem repeats or STRs
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.06,0:04:57.20,Chinese with background,,0,0,0,,这些片段被称为“短串联重复序列 (STR) ”
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.20,0:05:00.59,English with background,,0,0,0,,and different people have different numbers of repeats.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.20,0:05:00.59,Chinese with background,,0,0,0,,不同的人有不同数量的重复片段
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.59,0:05:03.03,English with background,,0,0,0,,Forensic labs produce STR profiles
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.59,0:05:03.03,Chinese with background,,0,0,0,,法医实验室通过计算所有的重复片段总数
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.03,0:05:06.95,English with background,,0,0,0,,by counting up the number of repeats at each location.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.03,0:05:06.95,Chinese with background,,0,0,0,,来生成STR档案
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.95,0:05:11.51,English,,0,0,0,,Initially, there were only 13 places on the DNA where STRs were counted,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.95,0:05:11.51,Chinese,,0,0,0,,最初  DNA 上只有13个位置的 STR 会被计数
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.51,0:05:15.09,English,,0,0,0,,but in 2017 that was expanded to 20.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.51,0:05:15.09,Chinese,,0,0,0,,但在2017年  这个数量扩大到了20个
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.09,0:05:18.00,English,,0,0,0,,It feels to me like that's not that much information.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.09,0:05:18.00,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我感觉这个档案并没有提供太多有用的信息
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.00,0:05:19.14,English,,0,0,0,,- It isn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.00,0:05:19.14,Chinese,,0,0,0,,-嗯  不多
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.14,0:05:21.04,English,,0,0,0,,- But the chances of two people having
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.14,0:05:21.04,Chinese,,0,0,0,,两个人在所有被计算的位置上 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.04,0:05:24.28,English,,0,0,0,,the exact same number of repeats at all locations
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.04,0:05:24.28,Chinese,,0,0,0,,都拥有相同数量的重复片段的概率
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.28,0:05:26.58,English,,0,0,0,,is incredibly small.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.28,0:05:26.58,Chinese,,0,0,0,,是非常小的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.58,0:05:28.78,English,,0,0,0,,The CODIS database now contains
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.58,0:05:28.78,Chinese,,0,0,0,,现在  CODIS 数据库中 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.78,0:05:32.09,English,,0,0,0,,over 18 million STR profiles.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.78,0:05:32.09,Chinese,,0,0,0,,已经有了超过1800万的 STR 档案
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.09,0:05:35.20,English,,0,0,0,,- The golden state killer's DNA profile has been up
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.09,0:05:35.20,Chinese,,0,0,0,,2001年  “金州杀手”的 DNA 档案
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.20,0:05:37.40,English,,0,0,0,,at the national DNA database
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.20,0:05:37.40,Chinese,,0,0,0,,就被上传到了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.40,0:05:41.17,English,,0,0,0,,that's run by the FBI called CODIS since 2001
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.40,0:05:41.17,Chinese,,0,0,0,,FBI 建立的国家 DNA 数据库 (CODIS) 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.17,0:05:44.97,English,,0,0,0,,and has been searching ever since with no hits.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.17,0:05:44.97,Chinese,,0,0,0,,自那以后  就一直在找他  但毫无成效
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.97,0:05:46.92,English,,0,0,0,,We did Interpol searching,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.97,0:05:46.92,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我们向国际刑警组织申请
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.92,0:05:50.03,English,,0,0,0,,trying to search other country's DNA databases thinking
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.92,0:05:50.03,Chinese,,0,0,0,,尝试在其他国家的 DNA 数据库中搜索  想着
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.03,0:05:53.00,English,,0,0,0,,well, maybe he came from a out of the country
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.03,0:05:53.00,Chinese,,0,0,0,,好吧  没准他来自其他国家
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.00,0:05:56.56,English,,0,0,0,,that's why after all this time we have yet to be able to identify him
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.00,0:05:56.56,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我们才一直没法确认他的身份
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.56,0:05:58.56,English,,0,0,0,,and obviously we didn't get any hits.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.56,0:05:58.56,Chinese,,0,0,0,,不过很显然  我们的搜索没有任何收获
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.26,0:06:04.01,English,,0,0,0,,- But genetic sequencing technology was advancing rapidly.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.26,0:06:04.01,Chinese,,0,0,0,,尽管如此  基因测序技术依然发展迅猛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.01,0:06:06.58,English,,0,0,0,,- [Female Reporter] The human genome project was completed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.01,0:06:06.58,Chinese,,0,0,0,,人类基因组计划已经完成
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.58,0:06:10.63,English,,0,0,0,,Since 1986 scientists had been mapping and sequencing
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.58,0:06:10.63,Chinese,,0,0,0,,从1986年开始  科学家们就一直在
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.63,0:06:15.28,English,,0,0,0,,the three billion nucleotides contained in the human genome.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.63,0:06:15.28,Chinese,,0,0,0,,绘制和测序人类基因组中的30亿个核苷酸
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.28,0:06:16.25,English,,0,0,0,,It's anticipated that
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.28,0:06:16.25,Chinese,,0,0,0,,这很让人期待……
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.25,0:06:19.24,English,,0,0,0,,- Soon private companies began offering genetic tests
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.25,0:06:19.24,Chinese,,0,0,0,,- 很快  私企就开始直接向消费者提供基因测序项目
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.24,0:06:23.56,English,,0,0,0,,directly to consumers and they provide far more genetic data
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.56,0:06:26.14,English,,0,0,0,,than what's in the CODIS database.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.24,0:06:26.14,Chinese,,0,0,0,,并向CODIS数据库直接提供更多的基因数据
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.14,0:06:27.73,English,,0,0,0,,I traveled to Houston, Texas
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.73,0:06:30.43,English,,0,0,0,,to visit Family Tree DNA headquarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.14,0:06:30.43,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我去到德州的波士顿  去拜访「家族族谱 DNA 公司」的总部
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.43,0:06:32.17,English,,0,0,0,,- We'll go in the lab and we'll start talking
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.17,0:06:34.63,English,,0,0,0,,about the life cycle of a sample.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.43,0:06:34.63,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我们会进到实验室  并就一个样本的生命周期进行探讨
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.63,0:06:35.51,English,,0,0,0,,There you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.63,0:06:35.51,Chinese,,0,0,0,,给你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.51,0:06:36.12,English,,0,0,0,,- Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.51,0:06:36.12,Chinese,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.12,0:06:38.98,English,,0,0,0,,These samples, what are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.12,0:06:38.98,Chinese,,0,0,0,,这些是什么的样本？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.98,0:06:41.03,English,,0,0,0,,- So they're cheek cells. They just scrape
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.98,0:06:41.03,Chinese,,0,0,0,,这些是脸部的细胞
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.03,0:06:43.24,English,,0,0,0,,the inside of their cheek, they put a cap on it
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.24,0:06:44.41,English,,0,0,0,,and they send it back to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.03,0:06:44.41,Chinese,,0,0,0,,人们就只是在他们的脸颊里面刮一下  用盖子盖上然后就送回给我们
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.41,0:06:46.05,English,,0,0,0,,- It's like a robot ballet.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.41,0:06:46.05,Chinese,,0,0,0,,- 它就像芭蕾舞机器人一样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.05,0:06:48.73,English,,0,0,0,,- Yes, so for DNA extraction,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.05,0:06:48.73,Chinese,,0,0,0,,- 是的  DNA 提取也是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.73,0:06:52.94,English,,0,0,0,,we need to remove all of the protections that are on the DNA
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.73,0:06:52.94,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我们要移除DNA上面的保护层  然后它自己就会分离出来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.94,0:06:58.52,English,,0,0,0,,and just separate it by itself so we can do testing on that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.94,0:06:58.52,Chinese,,0,0,0,,这样我们就能在它上面进行测试
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.41,0:07:02.09,English,,0,0,0,,- Instead of looking at 20 places on your DNA,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.41,0:07:02.09,Chinese,,0,0,0,,- 我们并不仅仅测试你 DNA 中的20个地方
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.09,0:07:06.07,English,,0,0,0,,these tests examined 700 to 800,000.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.09,0:07:06.07,Chinese,,0,0,0,,而是测试70到80万个
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.07,0:07:07.95,English,,0,0,0,,- The Family Finder test is based
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.95,0:07:10.05,English,,0,0,0,,on what's called a micro array
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.07,0:07:10.05,Chinese,,0,0,0,,- 寻找家人的 (基因) 测试是基于一个叫做微阵列的方式
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.05,0:07:12.37,English,,0,0,0,,and this is what a micro array looks like.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.05,0:07:12.37,Chinese,,0,0,0,,这就是微阵列看起来的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.37,0:07:15.56,English,,0,0,0,,Each one of those boxes is an individual.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.37,0:07:15.56,Chinese,,0,0,0,,这里面的每个格子代表一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.56,0:07:18.02,English,,0,0,0,,We can fit 24 individuals on here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.56,0:07:18.02,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我们能在这一片微阵列上放24个格子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.02,0:07:25.60,English,,0,0,0,,And within that box is about 710,000 positions of your DNA,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.02,0:07:25.60,Chinese,,0,0,0,,那在这个格子里面  是我们正在检查  从中获取数据的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.60,0:07:28.81,English,,0,0,0,,that we're measuring, we're getting data for.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.60,0:07:28.81,Chinese,,0,0,0,,你 DNA 中的大约71万个位置
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.81,0:07:30.44,English,,0,0,0,,- 710,000?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.81,0:07:30.44,Chinese,,0,0,0,,71万个？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.44,0:07:32.24,English,,0,0,0,,- Yes, and they're called snips.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.44,0:07:32.24,Chinese,,0,0,0,,对  它们叫片段
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.24,0:07:36.63,English,,0,0,0,,- So hang on, that's like 710,000
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.63,0:07:39.31,English,,0,0,0,,individual bases, like ATGC?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.24,0:07:39.31,Chinese,,0,0,0,,等等  所以  这里就是71万个片段  就像ATGC那样？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.31,0:07:40.14,English,,0,0,0,,- Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.31,0:07:40.14,Chinese,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.14,0:07:43.52,English,,0,0,0,,- For each person, you can measure 24 on that single chip?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.14,0:07:43.52,Chinese,,0,0,0,,对于每一个要求测试的人 您可以在这一个芯片上检查24个人的基因片段？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.52,0:07:44.90,English,,0,0,0,,- Correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.52,0:07:44.90,Chinese,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.90,0:07:48.74,English with background,,0,0,0,,- The human genome consists of three billion bases.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.90,0:07:48.74,Chinese with background,,0,0,0,,人的基因组中包含有300亿个碱基
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.74,0:07:53.74,English with background,,0,0,0,,All people share about 99.9% the exact same DNA,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.74,0:07:53.74,Chinese with background,,0,0,0,,而所有人类的 DNA 有99.9%是完全相同的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.16,0:07:57.49,English,,0,0,0,,which means on average, only about three million basis
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.49,0:07:59.58,English,,0,0,0,,differ from person to person.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.16,0:07:59.58,Chinese,,0,0,0,,这意味着  平均来说  人与人之间的基因只有300万个位置有差异
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.58,0:08:01.82,English,,0,0,0,,These individual letter changes are known
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.82,0:08:05.95,English,,0,0,0,,as single nucleotide polymorphisms or SNPs.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.58,0:08:05.95,Chinese,,0,0,0,,这种单个核酸的改变被称为单核苷酸多态性 (SNPs)
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.58,0:08:05.95,Chinese,,0,0,0,,{\an7\i1\pos(620,1290)}单核苷酸多态性{\fsp-24}：\N{\fsp0}DNA 序列中单个核苷酸的替代导致的{\fsp-24}、\N{\fsp0}且分布于种群中相当一部分个体 (如：1%以上) 中的基因多样性{\fsp-24}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.95,0:08:07.99,English,,0,0,0,,So on there, are there a whole bunch
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.99,0:08:10.52,English,,0,0,0,,of like little pieces of DNA then?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.95,0:08:10.52,Chinese,,0,0,0,,所以在这里就有一大堆那些小片的 DNA 那样吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.52,0:08:15.16,English,,0,0,0,,- Yes, so what we have is a short piece of DNA
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.16,0:08:17.81,English,,0,0,0,,that is specific to one SNP.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.52,0:08:17.81,Chinese,,0,0,0,,是的  我们这里的一个小片的 DNA  就是特定的一个多态单核苷酸
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.81,0:08:20.88,English,,0,0,0,,So it's one position in the genome
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.88,0:08:22.55,English,,0,0,0,,where we know there can be a difference.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.81,0:08:22.55,Chinese,,0,0,0,,所以  这是我们已知的  基因组内的一个能造成差异的位置
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.55,0:08:23.26,English,,0,0,0,,- Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.55,0:08:23.26,Chinese,,0,0,0,,这样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.26,0:08:26.79,English,,0,0,0,,Is there any example of a simple SNP
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.79,0:08:29.06,English,,0,0,0,,that confers some sort of?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.26,0:08:29.06,Chinese,,0,0,0,,能给我一个简单的单核苷酸多态性的例子吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.06,0:08:32.28,English,,0,0,0,,- Actually blue eyes is a single base change.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.06,0:08:32.28,Chinese,,0,0,0,,实际上蓝色眼睛是一个单基位的变化
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.28,0:08:32.70,English,,0,0,0,,- Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.28,0:08:32.70,Chinese,,0,0,0,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.70,0:08:33.34,English,,0,0,0,,- Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.70,0:08:33.34,Chinese,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.34,0:08:38.21,English,,0,0,0,,- So everyone with blue eyes has this one letter change? - mm hmm
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.34,0:08:38.21,Chinese,,0,0,0,,所以每一个有蓝眼睛的人都有这一个单基位变化？ - 嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.93,0:08:38.26,Chinese,,0,0,0,,{\pos(760,1646)}*其实可能有两处变化
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.21,0:08:41.35,English,,0,0,0,,- You can see now it's starting to scan the first box.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.21,0:08:41.35,Chinese,,0,0,0,,现在你能看到它从第一个格子开始扫描
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.03,0:08:48.85,English,,0,0,0,,- The results of your 710,000 SNPs can tell you
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.85,0:08:51.04,English,,0,0,0,,about your geographic ancestry
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.04,0:08:52.81,English,,0,0,0,,or possible medical conditions,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.03,0:08:52.81,Chinese,,0,0,0,,你的71万个多态单核苷酸 能让你知道你的地域性祖先 或者潜在的医疗状况
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.81,0:08:54.32,English,,0,0,0,,but they can also quantify
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.32,0:08:56.93,English,,0,0,0,,how related you are to someone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.81,0:08:56.93,Chinese,,0,0,0,,但它们也可以量化你和某个人的血缘关系程度
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.93,0:08:58.78,English,,0,0,0,,The genetics of having a kid
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.93,0:08:58.78,Chinese,,0,0,0,,产生后代的遗传学过程
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.78,0:09:02.34,English,,0,0,0,,are a bit like cutting two decks of cards together.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.78,0:09:02.34,Chinese,,0,0,0,,有点像把两沓扑克牌切在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.34,0:09:04.23,English,,0,0,0,,The resulting deck will share
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.34,0:09:04.23,Chinese,,0,0,0,,由此得到的后代
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.23,0:09:07.01,English,,0,0,0,,about half its cards with each parent
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.23,0:09:07.01,Chinese,,0,0,0,,与最初的两沓分别共享一半的卡牌
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.01,0:09:10.37,English,,0,0,0,,and there'll be long sequences of cards
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.01,0:09:10.37,Chinese,,0,0,0,,于是新牌堆中会有
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.37,0:09:15.15,English,,0,0,0,,which match identically sequences in each parent.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.37,0:09:15.15,Chinese,,0,0,0,,与父母一方完全相同的序列
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.15,0:09:19.40,English,,0,0,0,,Now, if this deck has a kid, well then
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.15,0:09:19.40,Chinese,,0,0,0,,现在如果他们有一个孩子  
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.40,0:09:24.70,English,,0,0,0,,its offspring will share only about a quarter of its cards with each grandparent
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.40,0:09:24.70,Chinese,,0,0,0,,这个孩子的祖父母和外祖父母  每人各占约1/4的卡牌
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.70,0:09:29.00,English,,0,0,0,,and the sections of identical cards will be shorter,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.70,0:09:29.00,Chinese,,0,0,0,,而相同卡牌组成的部分将会变得更短
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.00,0:09:31.91,English,,0,0,0,,and this is how it works with DNA.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.00,0:09:31.91,Chinese,,0,0,0,,这些规则也对DNA适用
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.91,0:09:33.94,English,,0,0,0,,The more closely you're related to someone,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.91,0:09:33.94,Chinese,,0,0,0,,你与某人的血缘关系越近
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.94,0:09:36.28,English,,0,0,0,,the more DNA you share and the longer
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.94,0:09:36.28,Chinese,,0,0,0,,你们共有的DNA就越多
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.28,0:09:38.70,English,,0,0,0,,the blocks of identical DNA are.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.28,0:09:38.70,Chinese,,0,0,0,,相同的 DNA 片段越长
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.70,0:09:41.18,English,,0,0,0,,But to compare the DNA of two people,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.70,0:09:41.18,Chinese,,0,0,0,,但是要比较两个人的DNA
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.18,0:09:43.60,English,,0,0,0,,you don't need to read every letter.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.18,0:09:43.60,Chinese,,0,0,0,,你不必遍历每一个碱基
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.60,0:09:45.70,English,,0,0,0,,The SNPs are sprinkled throughout the DNA
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.60,0:09:45.70,Chinese,,0,0,0,,SNP 在 DNA 中散布
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.70,0:09:48.12,English,,0,0,0,,roughly every 2000 bases.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.70,0:09:48.12,Chinese,,0,0,0,,大约每 2000 个碱基出现一次
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.12,0:09:51.42,English,,0,0,0,,So if you find long sections where the snips match up,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.12,0:09:51.42,Chinese,,0,0,0,,所以如果你发现 SNP 在一个长片段里对得上
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.42,0:09:55.46,English,,0,0,0,,you can bet that the DNA in between is identical too
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.42,0:09:55.46,Chinese,,0,0,0,,就可以认为两段 DNA 也完全相同
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.46,0:09:58.93,English,,0,0,0,,by comparing hundreds of thousands of snips sprinkled
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.46,0:09:58.93,Chinese,,0,0,0,,通过比较成百上千
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.93,0:10:00.11,English,,0,0,0,,throughout the DNA,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.93,0:10:00.11,Chinese,,0,0,0,,散布在 DNA 中的 SNP
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.11,0:10:03.74,English,,0,0,0,,you can see where these identical blocks start and stop
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.11,0:10:03.74,Chinese,,0,0,0,,你可以找到相同片段的起止点
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.74,0:10:06.64,English,,0,0,0,,and so how much total DNA is shared.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.74,0:10:06.64,Chinese,,0,0,0,,从而得知由多少 DNA 是共有的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.80,0:10:10.86,English,,0,0,0,,- Everywhere that is highlighted in blue
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.80,0:10:10.86,Chinese,,0,0,0,,- 随处可见用蓝色标出的就是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.86,0:10:13.36,English,,0,0,0,,is where I share DNA.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.86,0:10:13.36,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我共有的 DNA
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.38,0:10:16.00,English,,0,0,0,,- With your father? - With my father
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.38,0:10:16.00,Chinese,,0,0,0,,- 和你的父亲 - 和我的父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.00,0:10:17.74,English,,0,0,0,,which is exactly what you expect
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.00,0:10:17.74,Chinese,,0,0,0,,和预期的情况一样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.74,0:10:20.64,English,,0,0,0,,because I should share DNA with him everywhere
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.74,0:10:20.64,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我和他应该在各处都有相同的基因片段
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.64,0:10:24.24,English,,0,0,0,,because he gave me 50% of my DNA.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.64,0:10:24.24,Chinese,,0,0,0,,因为我遗传了他一半基因
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.24,0:10:25.73,English,,0,0,0,,So this is a second to third cousin.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.24,0:10:25.73,Chinese,,0,0,0,,这是我的再从兄弟或三从兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.73,0:10:28.23,English,,0,0,0,,I have no idea who this person is.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.73,0:10:28.23,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我不知道这个人是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.23,0:10:29.93,English,,0,0,0,,And you can see here,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.23,0:10:29.93,Chinese,,0,0,0,,你会发现
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.93,0:10:34.32,English,,0,0,0,,we are definitely not as closely related as me and my dad
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.93,0:10:34.32,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我们之间的血缘关系当然不像我和我父亲那样近
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.32,0:10:36.01,English,,0,0,0,,because where the blue is,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.32,0:10:36.01,Chinese,,0,0,0,,因为这些蓝色区域
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.01,0:10:38.20,English,,0,0,0,,those are the only regions of the chromosome
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.01,0:10:38.20,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我们仅在这些染色体区域
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.20,0:10:39.72,English,,0,0,0,,where we share DNA.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.20,0:10:39.72,Chinese,,0,0,0,,有相同的基因
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.63,0:10:42.84,English,,0,0,0,,- We all know that these genetic tests
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.63,0:10:42.84,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我们都知道这些遗传学检测
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.84,0:10:46.10,English,,0,0,0,,can help identify our relatives but the question is,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.84,0:10:46.10,Chinese,,0,0,0,,可以帮助我们找到亲属  但问题是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.10,0:10:50.00,English,,0,0,0,,can you do the same thing with law enforcement databases?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.10,0:10:50.00,Chinese,,0,0,0,,你能用执法者的数据库做到相同的事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.00,0:10:54.25,English,,0,0,0,,Can you identify family members using the CODIS database?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.00,0:10:54.25,Chinese,,0,0,0,,您能用 CODIS 数据库辨认家庭成员吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.25,0:10:56.24,English,,0,0,0,,- You can and it's only limited
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.25,0:10:56.24,Chinese,,0,0,0,,能  但不完全能
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.24,0:10:59.38,English,,0,0,0,,to really first order and second order relatives.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.24,0:10:59.38,Chinese,,0,0,0,,它只限于第一代和第二代亲属
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.38,0:11:02.57,English,,0,0,0,,- That means if I'm looking for the golden state killer,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.38,0:11:02.57,Chinese,,0,0,0,,这意味着如果我要寻找“金州杀手”
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.57,0:11:06.67,English,,0,0,0,,I'm looking for either his father, his brother or his son.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.57,0:11:06.67,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我是在找他的父亲  他的兄弟或者他的儿子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.67,0:11:11.28,English,,0,0,0,,We did that over and over again with no hits.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.67,0:11:11.28,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我们这样做了多次却一无所获
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.28,0:11:12.47,English,,0,0,0,,- Why is it so limited?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.28,0:11:12.47,Chinese,,0,0,0,,- 为什么它如此受限
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.47,0:11:15.22,English,,0,0,0,,- Because you've only got 23 loci.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.47,0:11:15.22,Chinese,,0,0,0,,- 因为你只检查23个基因位点
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.22,0:11:17.63,English,,0,0,0,,If you wanna do proper kinship analysis,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.22,0:11:17.63,Chinese,,0,0,0,,如果你想进行更好的血缘分析
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.63,0:11:21.85,English,,0,0,0,,you need to have more points assessed on that genome
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.63,0:11:21.85,Chinese,,0,0,0,,你需要测定基因组上的更多位置
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.85,0:11:24.24,English,,0,0,0,,to see how related you really are.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.85,0:11:24.24,Chinese,,0,0,0,,才能知道亲缘远近
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.24,0:11:27.19,English,,0,0,0,,- We know the answer is behind a locked door
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.24,0:11:27.19,Chinese,,0,0,0,,- 我们知道答案在一扇上锁的门后
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.19,0:11:28.73,English,,0,0,0,,and the answer is behind the locked door
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.19,0:11:31.45,Chinese,,0,0,0,,答案在 23andMe 和 Ancestry.com 的数据库中
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.73,0:11:31.45,English,,0,0,0,,of 23andMe and Ancestry.com.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.45,0:11:34.76,English,,0,0,0,,We know that they have millions of profiles.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.45,0:11:34.76,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我们知道他们有数以百万计的个人档案
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.76,0:11:38.21,English,,0,0,0,,Somebody related to him, a second cousin I would guess,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.76,0:11:38.21,Chinese,,0,0,0,,某个与他有关系的人也会在其中
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.21,0:11:39.04,English,,0,0,0,,would be in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.21,0:11:39.04,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我猜是他的从兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.04,0:11:40.14,English,,0,0,0,,- Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.04,0:11:40.14,Chinese,,0,0,0,,- 当然
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.14,0:11:43.50,English,,0,0,0,,- And that was very hard to deal with.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.14,0:11:43.50,Chinese,,0,0,0,,- 这处理起来相当困难
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.50,0:11:47.72,English,,0,0,0,,You know, that the answer is there behind this locked door.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.50,0:11:47.72,Chinese,,0,0,0,,答案就在那里 被锁在门后
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.72,0:11:50.14,English,,0,0,0,,- Law enforcement is not allowed to search
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.72,0:11:50.14,Chinese,,0,0,0,,执法者不被允许搜索
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.14,0:11:53.70,English,,0,0,0,,the databases of 23andMe and Ancestry.com
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.14,0:11:53.70,Chinese,,0,0,0,,23andMe 和 Ancestry.com 的数据库
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.70,0:11:57.98,English,,0,0,0,,but luckily for investigators, there was another way.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.70,0:11:57.98,Chinese,,0,0,0,,但是幸运的的是  对于调查员而言  还有另一条路可走
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.98,0:12:01.04,English,,0,0,0,,An independent website called GEDmatch had been set up
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.98,0:12:01.04,Chinese,,0,0,0,,有人建立了一个名为 GEDmatch 的独立网站
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.04,0:12:03.45,English,,0,0,0,,to allow people to connect with relatives.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.04,0:12:03.45,Chinese,,0,0,0,,使人们得以联系到自己的亲戚
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.45,0:12:04.67,English,,0,0,0,,You can upload the raw data
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.45,0:12:04.67,Chinese,,0,0,0,,你可以上传自己的原始 DNA 数据
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.67,0:12:07.12,English,,0,0,0,,from any of the big genetic testing companies
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.67,0:12:07.12,Chinese,,0,0,0,,无论它来自哪一间基因检测公司
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.12,0:12:08.95,English,,0,0,0,,and search for matches.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.12,0:12:08.95,Chinese,,0,0,0,,并搜索与自己基因相匹配的人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.95,0:12:12.68,English,,0,0,0,,- So when we initially search the GEDmatch database,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.95,0:12:12.68,Chinese,,0,0,0,,在我们开始搜索 GEDmatch 数据库时
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.68,0:12:15.49,English,,0,0,0,,our best hits come back at third cousins
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.68,0:12:15.49,Chinese,,0,0,0,,其中亲缘最近的  是他的三从兄弟(姐妹)
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.49,0:12:18.11,English,,0,0,0,,which means they shared you know, our top hit,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.49,0:12:18.11,Chinese,,0,0,0,,也就是说  这个人和他共享了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.11,0:12:20.65,English,,0,0,0,,I think shared about 1% of the DNA.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.11,0:12:20.65,Chinese,,0,0,0,,大约 1% 的 DNA
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.65,0:12:22.65,English,,0,0,0,,It's very little DNA that's shared
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.65,0:12:22.65,Chinese,,0,0,0,,他们共享的 DNA 确实很少
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.52,0:12:26.05,English,,0,0,0,,but that's a starting data point.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.52,0:12:26.05,Chinese,,0,0,0,,但这是数据的起点
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.05,0:12:31.37,English,,0,0,0,,And theoretically, by taking multiple of these individuals that share DNA
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.05,0:12:31.37,Chinese,,0,0,0,,理论上  通过获取多个共享 DNA 的个体
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.37,0:12:32.98,English,,0,0,0,,and building their family trees
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.37,0:12:32.98,Chinese,,0,0,0,,画出谱系图
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.98,0:12:36.20,English,,0,0,0,,using traditional genealogy and public source documents
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.98,0:12:36.20,Chinese,,0,0,0,,利用传统的基因学和公共来源的文件
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.20,0:12:38.19,English,,0,0,0,,like census records and obituaries
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.20,0:12:38.19,Chinese,,0,0,0,,比如人口普查记录  讣告
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.19,0:12:42.09,English,,0,0,0,,and newspaper articles and findagrave.com,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.19,0:12:42.09,Chinese,,0,0,0,,报刊文章和 findagrave.com
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.09,0:12:44.09,English,,0,0,0,,you build this family tree back
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.09,0:12:44.09,Chinese,,0,0,0,,就可以向上构建谱系图
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.09,0:12:47.60,English,,0,0,0,,until you get two of these relatives of the Golden State killer
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.09,0:12:47.60,Chinese,,0,0,0,,直到在“金州杀手”的亲属中找到这两个人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.60,0:12:49.32,English,,0,0,0,,you get them to intersect
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.60,0:12:49.32,Chinese,,0,0,0,,他们最终交会在同一处
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.32,0:12:51.16,English,,0,0,0,,where now you see, oh, they've got,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.32,0:12:51.16,Chinese,,0,0,0,,你会发现  哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.16,0:12:54.17,English,,0,0,0,,they share great-great grandparents together.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.16,0:12:54.17,Chinese,,0,0,0,,他们有共同的高祖父母
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.17,0:12:57.59,English,,0,0,0,,Theoretically the golden state killer is a descendant
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.17,0:12:57.59,Chinese,,0,0,0,,理论上  “金州杀手”也是他们的后代
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.59,0:12:59.67,English,,0,0,0,,from those same great-great grandparents.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.59,0:12:59.67,Chinese,,0,0,0,,来自相同的高祖父母
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.67,0:13:03.09,English,,0,0,0,,So once I identify that common ancestor,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.67,0:13:03.09,Chinese,,0,0,0,,所以  一旦我确认了他们共同的祖先
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.09,0:13:06.12,English,,0,0,0,,it's now identifying every single descendant
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.09,0:13:08.68,Chinese,,0,0,0,,接下来只要辨认这对高祖父母的每一个后代
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.12,0:13:08.68,English,,0,0,0,,from those great-great grandparents
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.68,0:13:10.84,English,,0,0,0,,and this becomes a huge process.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.68,0:13:10.84,Chinese,,0,0,0,,这是个巨大的工程
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.84,0:13:14.43,English,,0,0,0,,People in the 1840s would typically have 15 kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.84,0:13:14.43,Chinese,,0,0,0,,18世纪40年代的人通常有15个子女
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.43,0:13:16.83,English,,0,0,0,,You have to identify each of those kids
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.43,0:13:16.83,Chinese,,0,0,0,,你得逐个辨认他们的所有子女
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.83,0:13:18.27,English,,0,0,0,,and then all of their children
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.83,0:13:18.27,Chinese,,0,0,0,,还有这些子女的所有子女
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.27,0:13:19.72,English,,0,0,0,,and then all of their children.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.27,0:13:19.72,Chinese,,0,0,0,,依此类推
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.72,0:13:23.81,English,,0,0,0,,So now we have this exponentially growing family tree.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.72,0:13:23.81,Chinese,,0,0,0,,这样 就有了一张呈指数增长的谱系图
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.81,0:13:26.21,English,,0,0,0,,- How wide did that tree get?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.81,0:13:26.21,Chinese,,0,0,0,,这个谱系图会变得多宽呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.21,0:13:30.20,English,,0,0,0,,- I think we had over 1000 individuals in that family tree
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.21,0:13:30.20,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我估计有一千多人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.20,0:13:34.06,English,,0,0,0,,but we knew a lot about our offender.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.20,0:13:34.06,Chinese,,0,0,0,,但我们对这个罪犯十分了解
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.06,0:13:37.21,English,,0,0,0,,We were confident he was born between 1940 and 1960.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.06,0:13:37.21,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我们确信他生于20世纪40年代或50年代
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.21,0:13:38.67,English,,0,0,0,,We knew he was a white male.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.21,0:13:38.67,Chinese,,0,0,0,,他是白人男性
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.67,0:13:41.06,English,,0,0,0,,We knew he was 5'8" to 5'10".
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.67,0:13:41.06,Chinese,,0,0,0,,他的身高大约是1米73到1米78 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.06,0:13:42.45,English,,0,0,0,,You know, he's in California.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.06,0:13:42.45,Chinese,,0,0,0,,他人在加州
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.45,0:13:44.77,English,,0,0,0,,He's up in Sacramento in 1976.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.45,0:13:44.77,Chinese,,0,0,0,,1976年时  在萨克拉门托
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.77,0:13:47.49,English,,0,0,0,,He's in Southern California in the '80s
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.77,0:13:47.49,Chinese,,0,0,0,,20世纪80年代时  在南加州
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.49,0:13:50.95,English,,0,0,0,,and we basically narrowed it down to about five males
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.49,0:13:50.95,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我们最终将范围缩小到五个男性
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.95,0:13:52.88,English,,0,0,0,,and then it's just investigations.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.95,0:13:52.88,Chinese,,0,0,0,,然后就是调查了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.88,0:13:54.90,English,,0,0,0,,- With a suspect at their fingertips,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.88,0:13:54.90,Chinese,,0,0,0,,嫌疑人已经触手可及
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.90,0:13:56.32,English,,0,0,0,,this spring, they followed him
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.90,0:13:56.32,Chinese,,0,0,0,,今年春天  他们跟踪他
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.32,0:13:59.10,English,,0,0,0,,to a Sacramento area Hobby Lobby store
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.32,0:13:59.10,Chinese,,0,0,0,,前往萨克拉门托的 Hobby Lobby store
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.10,0:14:01.91,English,,0,0,0,,and took a DNA sample from his car door handle.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.10,0:14:01.91,Chinese,,0,0,0,,并从他的车门把手上采集到了他的 DNA 样本
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.91,0:14:05.90,English,,0,0,0,,Days later, investigators recovered another DNA sample
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.91,0:14:05.90,Chinese,,0,0,0,,几天后  调查人员找到了另一份 DNA 样本
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.90,0:14:09.32,English,,0,0,0,,from one discarded tissue which registered a match
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.90,0:14:09.32,Chinese,,0,0,0,,是从一张丢弃的纸巾上获得的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.32,0:14:12.27,English,,0,0,0,,to DNA evidence left at one of the crime scenes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.32,0:14:12.27,Chinese,,0,0,0,,它与其中一处犯罪现场遗留的 DNA 痕迹吻合
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.27,0:14:15.73,English,,0,0,0,,- Investigators in California say DNA evidence led them
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.27,0:14:15.73,Chinese,,0,0,0,,加州的调查人员说  DNA 痕迹引导他们
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.73,0:14:19.17,English,,0,0,0,,to one of the country's most notorious serial killers.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.73,0:14:19.17,Chinese,,0,0,0,,找到了美国最臭名昭著的连环杀手
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.17,0:14:23.56,English,,0,0,0,,Former police officer Joseph James DeAngelo was arrested yesterday
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.17,0:14:23.56,Chinese,,0,0,0,,前警官  约瑟夫·詹姆斯·德安杰罗  昨天被捕
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.56,0:14:28.20,English,,0,0,0,,and he is believed to be the so-called golden state killer.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.56,0:14:28.20,Chinese,,0,0,0,,据信  他就是所谓的“金州杀手”
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.20,0:14:32.83,English,,0,0,0,,For 44 years, countless investigators have worked it
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.20,0:14:32.83,Chinese,,0,0,0,,44年来  无数的调查员致力于破解此案
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.83,0:14:34.59,English,,0,0,0,,and have failed to solve it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.83,0:14:34.59,Chinese,,0,0,0,,无一成功
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.59,0:14:38.37,English,,0,0,0,,Within four and a half months, a team of six were able
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.59,0:14:38.37,Chinese,,0,0,0,,而一个六人小组  仅用四个半月
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.37,0:14:41.23,English,,0,0,0,,to figure out who the golden state killer was
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.37,0:14:43.01,Chinese,,0,0,0,,就能发现“金州杀手”原来是约瑟夫·德安杰罗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.23,0:14:43.01,English,,0,0,0,,and that was Joseph DeAngelo.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.01,0:14:45.91,English,,0,0,0,,- After the golden state killer was identified,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.01,0:14:45.91,Chinese,,0,0,0,,“金州杀手”被找到以后
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.91,0:14:49.54,English,,0,0,0,,the flood gates opened and we were seeing every week
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.91,0:14:49.54,Chinese,,0,0,0,,如闸门打开一般  我们每周都能看到
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.54,0:14:53.28,English,,0,0,0,,not only single killers, but multiple killers, serial killers
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.54,0:14:53.28,Chinese,,0,0,0,,不只是单人杀手  还有多人杀手  连环杀手
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.28,0:14:55.23,English,,0,0,0,,every week were being identified
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.28,0:14:55.23,Chinese,,0,0,0,,每周都有新的凶手被辨认出来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.23,0:14:57.51,English,,0,0,0,,from cases in the '70s and the '80s.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.23,0:14:57.51,Chinese,,0,0,0,,那些七八十年代的悬案得以破解
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.51,0:14:59.65,English,,0,0,0,,- 'Cause, there's been over 70 cases now
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.51,0:14:59.65,Chinese,,0,0,0,,因此  调查人员现在用这种方式
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.65,0:15:01.47,English,,0,0,0,,that they've solved this way
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.65,0:15:01.47,Chinese,,0,0,0,,解决了超过70件案子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.47,0:15:05.30,English,,0,0,0,,and they continue to solve them at a fairly regular rate
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.47,0:15:05.30,Chinese,,0,0,0,,并且他们依然以一种相当稳定的速率解决案件
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.30,0:15:06.35,English,,0,0,0,,and I think
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.30,0:15:06.35,Chinese,,0,0,0,,并且我认为
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.35,0:15:08.72,English,,0,0,0,,- Presumably that rate's just gonna increase.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.35,0:15:08.72,Chinese,,0,0,0,,很有可能这一速率只会增加
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.72,0:15:09.16,English,,0,0,0,,- Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.72,0:15:09.16,Chinese,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.16,0:15:12.06,English,,0,0,0,,- And there's gonna be more because it's working
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.16,0:15:12.06,Chinese,,0,0,0,,并且将会有更多  因为这种方法是有效的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.06,0:15:16.67,English,,0,0,0,,and we are going to help find these people.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.06,0:15:16.67,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我们将会帮忙找寻这些人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.67,0:15:18.51,English,,0,0,0,,- But the scary thing is in the US,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.67,0:15:18.51,Chinese,,0,0,0,,但是可怕的是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.51,0:15:21.29,English,,0,0,0,,you have 100,000 cold case murders with DNA.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.51,0:15:21.29,Chinese,,0,0,0,,全美一共有100000起留有DNA的谋杀悬案
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.29,0:15:24.05,English,,0,0,0,,You have more cold cases but the ones with DNA
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.29,0:15:24.05,Chinese,,0,0,0,,总计的谋杀悬案有更多
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.05,0:15:25.95,English,,0,0,0,,is estimated about 100,000
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.05,0:15:25.95,Chinese,,0,0,0,,但是留有DNA的估计在100000起左右
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.95,0:15:30.20,English,,0,0,0,,There's roughly about 650,000 sexual assaults,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.95,0:15:30.20,Chinese,,0,0,0,,大约有650000起留有 DNA 的性侵犯悬案
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.20,0:15:32.39,English,,0,0,0,,cold cases with DNA. - With DNA?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.20,0:15:32.39,Chinese,,0,0,0,,留有DNA？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.39,0:15:34.41,English,,0,0,0,,It seems like a real paradigm shift.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.39,0:15:34.41,Chinese,,0,0,0,,这似乎像是真正的范式转变
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.41,0:15:35.24,English,,0,0,0,,- It is.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.41,0:15:35.24,Chinese,,0,0,0,,确实是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.24,0:15:37.80,English,,0,0,0,,Multiple law enforcement agencies has said
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.24,0:15:37.80,Chinese,,0,0,0,,许多执法部门认为
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.80,0:15:42.80,English,,0,0,0,,that this is the most revolutionary tool they've had
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.80,0:15:42.80,Chinese,,0,0,0,,这是他们继采用指纹之后
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.90,0:15:45.58,English,,0,0,0,,since the adoption of the fingerprint.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.90,0:15:45.58,Chinese,,0,0,0,,用过的最具革命性的工具
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.58,0:15:50.10,English,,0,0,0,,- With traditional DNA, it required getting a sample
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.58,0:15:50.10,Chinese,,0,0,0,,对传统DNA技术来说  它需要从实际个体
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.10,0:15:51.58,English,,0,0,0,,from the actual individual.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.10,0:15:51.58,Chinese,,0,0,0,,获取样本
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.58,0:15:54.80,English,,0,0,0,,It's a one-to-one type of process.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.58,0:15:54.80,Chinese,,0,0,0,,这是一种一对一的过程
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.80,0:15:57.23,English,,0,0,0,,And so these offenders who let's say
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.80,0:15:57.23,Chinese,,0,0,0,,所以这些罪犯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.23,0:15:59.09,English,,0,0,0,,they have committed crimes and haven't been caught
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.23,0:15:59.09,Chinese,,0,0,0,,假设他们犯了罪且从未被抓
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.09,0:16:02.21,English,,0,0,0,,and they're just living their life and they're thinking,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.09,0:16:02.21,Chinese,,0,0,0,,之后他们过着自己的生活  心里想着
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.21,0:16:05.62,English,,0,0,0,,well, my DNA has never been taken from me. So they may..
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.21,0:16:05.62,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我从来没被提取过DNA
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.62,0:16:07.16,English,,0,0,0,,I may have left DNA in the case
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.62,0:16:07.16,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我可能在1975年犯下的案子里
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.16,0:16:10.06,English,,0,0,0,,that I committed back in 1975,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.16,0:16:10.06,Chinese,,0,0,0,,留下了我的DNA
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.06,0:16:13.49,English,,0,0,0,,but they've never gotten my DNA, they won't find me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.06,0:16:13.49,Chinese,,0,0,0,,但是执法部门没有我的DNA  他们找不到我的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.49,0:16:16.22,English,,0,0,0,,But now we don't have to rely upon that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.49,0:16:16.22,Chinese,,0,0,0,,但是现在我们不必依赖传统DNA技术了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.22,0:16:19.47,English,,0,0,0,,Somebody distantly related to that offender
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.22,0:16:19.47,Chinese,,0,0,0,,如果罪犯的某个远房亲戚
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.47,0:16:22.54,English,,0,0,0,,has put their DNA into a database
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.47,0:16:22.54,Chinese,,0,0,0,,将自己的 DNA 录入数据库中
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.54,0:16:24.69,English,,0,0,0,,and they have to start getting nervous
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.54,0:16:24.69,Chinese,,0,0,0,,罪犯就不得不开始紧张了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.69,0:16:26.36,English,,0,0,0,,because that's outside of their control.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.69,0:16:26.36,Chinese,,0,0,0,,因为这件事不是他们能控制的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.36,0:16:29.09,English,,0,0,0,,They can't account for a third cousin
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.36,0:16:29.09,Chinese,,0,0,0,,他们无法了解自己的三从兄弟姐妹的情况
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.09,0:16:31.56,English,,0,0,0,,or what that third cousin is doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.09,0:16:31.56,Chinese,,0,0,0,,也不知道他们在做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.56,0:16:33.14,English,,0,0,0,,And so they start getting nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.56,0:16:33.14,Chinese,,0,0,0,,所以开始紧张不安
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.14,0:16:34.11,English,,0,0,0,,And I've kind of wondered
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.14,0:16:34.11,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我有些好奇
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.11,0:16:37.18,English,,0,0,0,,how many of these individuals recognize
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.11,0:16:37.18,Chinese,,0,0,0,,这些罪犯中有多少人会意识到
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.18,0:16:38.98,English,,0,0,0,,that law enforcement is eventually gonna
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.18,0:16:38.98,Chinese,,0,0,0,,因为自己的某个三从兄弟姐妹将他们自己的 DNA 放入数据库
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.98,0:16:40.88,English,,0,0,0,,be knocking on their door as a result
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.98,0:16:40.88,Chinese,,0,0,0,,最终会导致执法者
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.88,0:16:43.93,English,,0,0,0,,of a third cousin putting their DNA in the database?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.88,0:16:43.93,Chinese,,0,0,0,,敲响他们的房门
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.93,0:16:47.81,English,,0,0,0,,- Each person who uploads their information to a database
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.93,0:16:47.81,Chinese,,0,0,0,,每个将自己信息上传数据库的人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.81,0:16:49.60,English,,0,0,0,,illuminates the identities
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.81,0:16:49.60,Chinese,,0,0,0,,将示明他们周围
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.60,0:16:52.41,English,,0,0,0,,of hundreds of other people around them,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.60,0:16:52.41,Chinese,,0,0,0,,数百个人的身份
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.41,0:16:56.26,English,,0,0,0,,parents, siblings, aunts, and uncles and cousins.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.41,0:16:56.26,Chinese,,0,0,0,,父母、兄弟姐妹、姑姑、叔叔和堂兄弟姐妹们
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.26,0:17:01.00,English,,0,0,0,,A study by ancestry DNA found the average person in the UK
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.26,0:17:01.00,Chinese,,0,0,0,,一项对祖先 DNA 的研究发现 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.00,0:17:06.00,English,,0,0,0,,has 175 third cousins and it doesn't stop there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.00,0:17:06.00,Chinese,,0,0,0,,英国人平均有175个三从兄弟姐妹  而且还不止于此
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.50,0:17:09.64,English,,0,0,0,,The DNA in one person will be shared
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.50,0:17:09.64,Chinese,,0,0,0,,一人身上的 DNA
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.64,0:17:13.04,English,,0,0,0,,by hundreds of people yet to be born.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.64,0:17:13.04,Chinese,,0,0,0,,将共享给数百个尚未出生的人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.04,0:17:16.66,English,,0,0,0,,Children, grandchildren, nieces, and nephews,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.04,0:17:16.66,Chinese,,0,0,0,,子女  孙子/孙女  侄子/侄女  外甥/外甥女
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.66,0:17:19.62,English,,0,0,0,,and cousins once or twice removed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.66,0:17:19.62,Chinese,,0,0,0,,甚至是差一个或者是两个辈分的表亲
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.62,0:17:23.41,English,,0,0,0,,Realistically, each person shares identifiable DNA
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.62,0:17:23.41,Chinese,,0,0,0,,现实中 每个人都与过去与未来的近1000人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.41,0:17:28.21,English,,0,0,0,,with nearly 1000 people past and future.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.41,0:17:28.21,Chinese,,0,0,0,,共享可被识别的 DNA
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.21,0:17:31.03,English,,0,0,0,,So it doesn't take many people uploading their data
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.21,0:17:31.03,Chinese,,0,0,0,,不需要许多人上传他们的数据
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.03,0:17:35.47,English,,0,0,0,,to reveal the identities of everyone living in a country.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.03,0:17:35.47,Chinese,,0,0,0,,就能显示出生活在一个国家的所有人的身份
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.47,0:17:39.61,English,,0,0,0,,Back in 2018, a study found that using an existing database
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.47,0:17:39.61,Chinese,,0,0,0,,在2018年 一项研究发现
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.61,0:17:44.52,English,,0,0,0,,of just 1.3 million people, they could identify 60%
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.61,0:17:44.52,Chinese,,0,0,0,,使用现存的130万人口的数据库 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.52,0:17:47.34,English,,0,0,0,,of all Americans of European descent.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.52,0:17:47.34,Chinese,,0,0,0,,他们能够确认出60%的欧裔美国人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.34,0:17:49.34,English,,0,0,0,,And they estimated with a database containing
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.34,0:17:49.34,Chinese,,0,0,0,,他们仅仅是用包含了人口总数的2%的数据库
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.34,0:17:53.34,English,,0,0,0,,just 2% of the population, you could find a third cousin
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.34,0:17:53.34,Chinese,,0,0,0,,进行估计 就能在99%的测试例中找到
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.34,0:17:57.25,English,,0,0,0,,or closer match in 99% of cases.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.34,0:17:57.25,Chinese,,0,0,0,,三从兄弟姐妹或者更亲的血缘关系
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.12,0:18:01.53,English,,0,0,0,,- DNA storage is one of the things that we have
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.12,0:18:01.53,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我们拥有的DNA存储
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.53,0:18:04.09,English,,0,0,0,,that is really unlike anything else.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.53,0:18:04.09,Chinese,,0,0,0,,和其他东西完全不同
