Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.19,0:19:38.50,Chinese,,0,0,0,,然后保费猛涨
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.50,0:19:42.87,English,,0,0,0,,That's the biggest place that I see as a privacy concern.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.50,0:19:42.87,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我认为这是最关乎个人隐私的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.87,0:19:44.66,English,,0,0,0,,- Once your genetic information is out there,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.87,0:19:44.66,Chinese,,0,0,0,,- 一旦你的基因信息被获取
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.66,0:19:45.26,English,,0,0,0,,it's out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.66,0:19:45.26,Chinese,,0,0,0,,它就会一直保存在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.26,0:19:47.37,English,,0,0,0,,It's not like a credit card where you can get a new one.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.26,0:19:47.37,Chinese,,0,0,0,,这可不像信用卡  你能办一张新的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.37,0:19:48.69,English,,0,0,0,,Yeah you're giving away something
