Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.90,0:19:55.38,English,,0,0,0,,in the first place. - Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.90,0:19:55.38,Chinese,,0,0,0,,并不是我们自己的 - 的确
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.38,0:19:57.93,English,,0,0,0,,- Our information is shared.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.38,0:19:57.93,Chinese,,0,0,0,,- 我们的信息是共享的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.93,0:19:59.55,English,,0,0,0,,- Yes with your relatives.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.93,0:19:59.55,Chinese,,0,0,0,,- 与我们的亲属
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.55,0:20:02.01,English,,0,0,0,,- Yes. - And although you may be
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.55,0:20:02.01,Chinese,,0,0,0,,- 是的 - 并且即使你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.01,0:20:03.48,English,,0,0,0,,adverse to this sort of thing,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.01,0:20:03.48,Chinese,,0,0,0,,厌恶这种东西
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.48,0:20:06.11,English,,0,0,0,,if they've already done it, if it,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.48,0:20:06.11,Chinese,,0,0,0,,如果他们已经做了检测
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.11,0:20:08.79,English,,0,0,0,,you know, in a way you're out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.11,0:20:08.79,Chinese,,0,0,0,,那么你懂的  某种意义上你已经在数据库中了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.79,0:20:11.77,English,,0,0,0,,- In society today, you have very clearly had two camps.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.79,0:20:11.77,Chinese,,0,0,0,,- 当今社会已经分成了两个阵营
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.77,0:20:14.28,English,,0,0,0,,There are those that are very comfortable
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.77,0:20:14.28,Chinese,,0,0,0,,那些非常愿意
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.28,0:20:17.50,English,,0,0,0,,having their genome available to be able to be searched
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.28,0:20:17.50,Chinese,,0,0,0,,把自己的基因组交由执法者
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.50,0:20:18.88,English,,0,0,0,,for law enforcement purposes
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.50,0:20:18.88,Chinese,,0,0,0,,进行相关搜索的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.88,0:20:21.64,English,,0,0,0,,and there are others that are not comfortable at all
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.88,0:20:21.64,Chinese,,0,0,0,,以及其他对此感到非常不适的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.64,0:20:23.44,English,,0,0,0,,and that's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.64,0:20:23.44,Chinese,,0,0,0,,这是人之常情
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.44,0:20:25.49,English,,0,0,0,,- The problem is of course,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.44,0:20:25.49,Chinese,,0,0,0,,- 问题当然是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.49,0:20:28.07,English,,0,0,0,,those people who don't want theirs to be searchable
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.49,0:20:28.07,Chinese,,0,0,0,,那些不想让自己可被搜索的人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.07,0:20:30.69,English,,0,0,0,,could have their DNA uploaded inadvertently
