Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.69,0:20:32.39,English,,0,0,0,,by their relatives.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.69,0:20:32.39,Chinese,,0,0,0,,不经意上传了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.39,0:20:33.38,English,,0,0,0,,Do you know what I mean?
