Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.38,0:20:35.73,English,,0,0,0,,So like, if I don't want my DNA
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.38,0:20:35.73,Chinese,,0,0,0,,所以  如果我不想让执法者搜索
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.73,0:20:37.21,English,,0,0,0,,to be searchable by law enforcement
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.73,0:20:37.21,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我的 DNA
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.21,0:20:39.66,English,,0,0,0,,but my sister uploads hers, - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.21,0:20:39.66,Chinese,,0,0,0,,但是我妹妹上传了她的 - 是的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.66,0:20:43.46,English,,0,0,0,,- It's almost as good as me doing it myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.66,0:20:43.46,Chinese,,0,0,0,,- 这和我自己上传效果几乎一样
