Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.15,0:20:50.85,English,,0,0,0,,is we only accept samples from law enforcement
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.15,0:20:50.85,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我们只在某些情况下接受
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.85,0:20:52.72,English,,0,0,0,,under certain circumstances.
