Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.84,0:21:12.56,English,,0,0,0,,so that they can try to find out who the abductor is.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.84,0:21:12.56,Chinese,,0,0,0,,这样执法者就可能找到绑匪
