Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.18,0:21:45.75,Chinese,,0,0,0,,- 有人破门而入
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.75,0:21:48.52,English,,0,0,0,,and assaulted her.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.75,0:21:48.52,Chinese,,0,0,0,,袭击了她
