Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.79,0:22:25.62,Chinese,,0,0,0,,- 他们接下了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.67,0:22:29.01,English,,0,0,0,,- They subsequently caught the individual
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.67,0:22:29.01,Chinese,,0,0,0,,随后警方根据 GEDmatch 中的检索结果
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.01,0:22:32.45,English,,0,0,0,,from that search that they performed on GEDmatch.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.01,0:22:32.45,Chinese,,0,0,0,,抓到了犯罪嫌疑人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.56,0:22:38.04,English,,0,0,0,,- But people within the genealogy world kinda got
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.56,0:22:38.04,Chinese,,0,0,0,,- 但是做家谱分析的人们
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.04,0:22:41.46,English,,0,0,0,,their passions and flame saying that is stepping outside
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.04,0:22:41.46,Chinese,,0,0,0,,非常愤怒  他们说这已经超出了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.46,0:22:43.21,English,,0,0,0,,of what this tool should be used for
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.46,0:22:43.21,Chinese,,0,0,0,,这个工具本应被使用的范围
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.21,0:22:46.28,English,,0,0,0,,and they ended up putting a lot of pressure on GEDmatch.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.21,0:22:46.28,Chinese,,0,0,0,,他们最终向 GEDmatch 施加了很多压力
