Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.23,0:22:55.33,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我觉得这到最后反而是一件好事
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.33,0:22:56.63,English,,0,0,0,,Everybody got zeroed out
