Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.63,0:22:59.06,Chinese,,0,0,0,,然后他们会注册回来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.06,0:23:04.00,English,,0,0,0,,- Subsequently GEDmatch was sold to Verogen.
