Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.00,0:23:06.38,English,,0,0,0,,- I can tell you a new user today
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.00,0:23:06.38,Chinese,,0,0,0,,- 我可以说  目前的新用户
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.38,0:23:10.44,English,,0,0,0,,when they sign up for GEDmatch, about 73% of them
