Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.44,0:23:14.17,English,,0,0,0,,are signing up to allow law enforcement to search.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.44,0:23:14.17,Chinese,,0,0,0,,允许执法者检索数据
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.17,0:23:15.31,English,,0,0,0,,We're pretty happy with that.
