Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.57,0:23:25.04,English,,0,0,0,,You know what I mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.57,0:23:25.04,Chinese,,0,0,0,,懂我意思吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.04,0:23:27.15,English,,0,0,0,,You don't know that many of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.04,0:23:27.15,Chinese,,0,0,0,,你对他们不很了解
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.15,0:23:31.55,English,,0,0,0,,Without even knowing it, you're helping justice.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.15,0:23:31.55,Chinese,,0,0,0,,你在不知不觉中协助了正义的一方
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.55,0:23:36.33,English,,0,0,0,,You're helping a victim's family get a little bit of peace,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.55,0:23:36.33,Chinese,,0,0,0,,你在帮助受害者的家庭获得一点宽慰
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.33,0:23:38.73,English,,0,0,0,,not closure, but a little bit of peace
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.33,0:23:38.73,Chinese,,0,0,0,,不是悲痛的终结  只是一点平静
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.73,0:23:39.82,English,,0,0,0,,and why not? - They get an answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.73,0:23:39.82,Chinese,,0,0,0,,为什么不呢 - 他们有自己的答案
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.82,0:23:41.40,English,,0,0,0,,- Partly, you could make an argument
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.82,0:23:41.40,Chinese,,0,0,0,,- 在一定程度上  你可以这样认为
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.40,0:23:46.36,English,,0,0,0,,that if you wanna be an activist helping catch criminals,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.40,0:23:46.36,Chinese,,0,0,0,,如果你想成为一名帮助抓捕犯罪分子的热心市民
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.36,0:23:47.70,English,,0,0,0,,one of the best things you can do
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.36,0:23:47.70,Chinese,,0,0,0,,你能做到的最好的事情之一
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.70,0:23:52.02,English,,0,0,0,,is encourage everyone you know to be tested
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.70,0:23:52.02,Chinese,,0,0,0,,就是鼓励身边的每个人都接受DNA测试
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.02,0:23:53.30,English,,0,0,0,,and put in the database.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.02,0:23:53.30,Chinese,,0,0,0,,并将基因录入数据库
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.30,0:23:57.33,English,,0,0,0,,- Correct and you know, there are millions
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.30,0:23:57.33,Chinese,,0,0,0,,- 的确 如你所知
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.33,0:24:02.81,English,,0,0,0,,of people who have tested at other companies that are not working with law enforcement.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.33,0:24:02.81,Chinese,,0,0,0,,还有数百万人在不与执法部门合作的公司做了测试
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.81,0:24:06.97,English,,0,0,0,,And if they want to help, all they have to do
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.81,0:24:06.97,Chinese,,0,0,0,,如果他们想要提供帮助
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.97,0:24:12.43,English,,0,0,0,,is download their raw data and they can upload it for free into our database.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.97,0:24:12.43,Chinese,,0,0,0,,他们只需要下载原始数据  并将其免费上传至我们的数据库
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.43,0:24:16.35,English,,0,0,0,,- I absolutely believe in a person's right to privacy.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.43,0:24:16.35,Chinese,,0,0,0,,- 我完全相信人们的隐私权
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.35,0:24:19.01,English,,0,0,0,,But I also absolutely believe we have a right not
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.35,0:24:19.01,Chinese,,0,0,0,,但是我也完全相信
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.01,0:24:21.54,English,,0,0,0,,to get murdered or sexually assaulted or it will be part
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.01,0:24:21.54,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我们有权不被谋杀或性侵
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.54,0:24:25.31,English,,0,0,0,,having violent crimes committed against us.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.54,0:24:25.31,Chinese,,0,0,0,,否则相同的事情可能会落到我们头上
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.31,0:24:27.82,English,,0,0,0,,There has to be an equal balance.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.31,0:24:27.82,Chinese,,0,0,0,,这中间必须做出权衡
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.82,0:24:31.11,English,,0,0,0,,- That scale of my privacy has been taken
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.82,0:24:31.11,Chinese,,0,0,0,,- 这是个平衡如果你认为你的隐私被侵犯了 
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.11,0:24:33.65,English,,0,0,0,,because of a third cousin has been identified
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.11,0:24:33.65,Chinese,,0,0,0,,因为你的三从兄弟姐妹上传了DNA信息 
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.65,0:24:37.01,English,,0,0,0,,versus a mother who's talking about her daughter has been murdered,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.65,0:24:37.01,Chinese,,0,0,0,,这个相比于一位女儿被谋杀了的母亲 
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.01,0:24:40.21,English,,0,0,0,,that scale is way the hell like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.01,0:24:40.21,Chinese,,0,0,0,,这个平衡不用说都知道隐私在这里啥也算不上
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.21,0:24:43.54,English,,0,0,0,,- We're at a point now where in many ways technology
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.21,0:24:43.54,Chinese,,0,0,0,,- 在许多方面，我们现在的科技发展
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.54,0:24:47.62,English,,0,0,0,,has kind of outstripped where the laws are.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.54,0:24:47.62,Chinese,,0,0,0,,已经超过了现有法律的有效范围
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.62,0:24:49.00,English,,0,0,0,,I truly believe
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.62,0:24:49.00,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我真希望
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.00,0:24:56.56,English,,0,0,0,,that ultimately this tool and the, all the concerns with it will probably end up
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.00,0:24:56.56,Chinese,,0,0,0,,这项技术  以及所有相关的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.56,0:24:58.71,English,,0,0,0,,in front of the nation Supreme Court
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.56,0:24:58.71,Chinese,,0,0,0,,最终都会提交给国家最高法院
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.71,0:25:00.31,English,,0,0,0,,and there will be a decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.71,0:25:00.31,Chinese,,0,0,0,,并且会有个结果
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.31,0:25:03.70,English,,0,0,0,,My bottom line message, if you're gonna make a decision,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.31,0:25:03.70,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我的底线是  如果你要做个判决
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.70,0:25:06.60,English,,0,0,0,,if there's gonna be laws restricting law enforcement to use it,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.70,0:25:06.60,Chinese,,0,0,0,,如果这事涉及到法律的制裁
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.60,0:25:09.80,English,,0,0,0,,make sure that you're making an informed decision
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.60,0:25:09.80,Chinese,,0,0,0,,请确保你做出明智的决定
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.80,0:25:12.89,English,,0,0,0,,and not assuming what it is based on
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.80,0:25:12.89,Chinese,,0,0,0,,而不是根据 DNA 和遗传学来猜测
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.89,0:25:15.45,English,,0,0,0,,its DNA and genetics and law enforcement
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.89,0:25:15.45,Chinese,,0,0,0,,并将“罪犯”绳之以法
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.45,0:25:18.37,English,,0,0,0,,because it really isn't what you think it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.45,0:25:18.37,Chinese,,0,0,0,,因为它真的不是你想象的那样
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.37,0:25:20.31,English,,0,0,0,,- I gotta keep a couple of million people happy
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.37,0:25:20.31,Chinese,,0,0,0,,- 从某种意义上说  我得让几百万人开心
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.31,0:25:23.97,English,,0,0,0,,so that I have access to the identities, kind of in a sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.31,0:25:23.97,Chinese,,0,0,0,,才能拥有这些人的身份 (在此指基因) 
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.97,0:25:25.66,English,,0,0,0,,- In a sense, right? - Of millions,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.97,0:25:25.66,Chinese,,0,0,0,,- 某种意义上  对吧？- 几百万
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.66,0:25:26.95,English,,0,0,0,,of hundreds of millions of people.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.66,0:25:26.95,Chinese,,0,0,0,,几亿人
