Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.45,0:25:32.58,English,,0,0,0,,These are people who are willing to give up their information
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.45,0:25:32.58,Chinese,,0,0,0,,这是那些愿意放弃他们的信息的人
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.58,0:25:33.15,English,,0,0,0,,- Give up, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.58,0:25:33.15,Chinese,,0,0,0,,- 是的  放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.15,0:25:34.92,English,,0,0,0,,- To find their ancestors. - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.15,0:25:34.92,Chinese,,0,0,0,,- 来寻找他们的祖先  - 对
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.92,0:25:37.67,English,,0,0,0,,- There may be many others who are militantly private
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.92,0:25:37.67,Chinese,,0,0,0,,- 还有许多其他非常注重隐私的人
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.67,0:25:40.06,English,,0,0,0,,but they don't get a say in the decision
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.67,0:25:40.06,Chinese,,0,0,0,,但是他们对于
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.06,0:25:42.81,English,,0,0,0,,of whether they're gonna be searchable
