Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.81,0:25:44.57,English,,0,0,0,,through that person or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.81,0:25:44.57,Chinese,,0,0,0,,并没有发言权
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.57,0:25:47.53,English,,0,0,0,,- True, that's the choice you make.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.57,0:25:47.53,Chinese,,0,0,0,,- 是的  这是你的决定
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.38,0:25:49.88,English,,0,0,0,,- That's the choice you don't make.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.38,0:25:49.88,Chinese,,0,0,0,,- 这是你不会做出的决定
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.88,0:25:52.52,English,,0,0,0,,- It's a choice you don't make but it's also
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.88,0:25:52.52,Chinese,,0,0,0,,- 你也不会选择这样
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.52,0:25:54.72,English,,0,0,0,,it's the choice we have to make as a society,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.52,0:25:54.72,Chinese,,0,0,0,,但这也是我们作为一个社会必须做出的选择
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.72,0:25:56.35,English,,0,0,0,,is what's that balance.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.72,0:25:56.35,Chinese,,0,0,0,,这种平衡是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.35,0:25:58.34,English,,0,0,0,,There is always gonna be winners and loses
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.35,0:25:58.34,Chinese,,0,0,0,,在我看来
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.34,0:25:59.17,English,,0,0,0,,in my mind, right?
